claim.claim-text:
A floor panel (10) for an airborne vehicle (20), comprising:
a controller housing (9);
a first heated panel (6) configured to heat the floor panel (10);
a panel connector (11) arranged in a wall of the controller housing (9);
at least one power line (11b, 11c) coupled between the panel connector (11) and the first heated panel (6) and
configured to supply electric power, which is input to the panel connector (11), to the first heated panel (6);
a switch (3) connected in one of the power lines (11b, 11c); and
a microcontroller (1) connected to the switch (3) and configured to actuate the switch (3) for interrupting the electric power supply to the first heated panel (6) in case of an electric fault in the floor panel (10).
